<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- AMY'S STORY                                 -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="about-story convo-reveal-group">
  <div class="about-story__inner">
    <div class="convo-reveal">
      <div class="convo-speaker">
        <div class="convo-speaker__dot"></div>
        The founder
      </div>
      <div class="convo-divider"></div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="convo-heading convo-reveal">
      Built for brains like ours<span class="convo-cursor"></span>
    </h2>

    <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
      I'm Amy — a <strong>Neurodivergent artist</strong> with no tech background, turned creative technologist.
    </p>

    <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
      Having jumped into AI with the dawn of ChatGPT, I found myself exceptionally capable of orchestrating and building with multiple AIs — leading to the founding of <strong>Multiplist</strong>.
    </p>

    <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
      After years of losing my best thinking inside AI chat threads, I built the system I needed: a meaning operating system that extracts and organizes everything important from your conversations. The insights don't disappear anymore. The decisions stay. The frameworks compound.
    </p>

    <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
      Now I set this up for creative teams who can't afford to keep losing their collective intelligence. <strong>Multiplist Studios</strong> is the consulting practice — one engagement can transform how you work with AI forever.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- WHAT WE BELIEVE                             -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="convo-section convo-reveal-group">
  <div class="convo-reveal">
    <div class="convo-speaker">
      <div class="convo-speaker__dot"></div>
      What we believe
    </div>
    <div class="convo-divider"></div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="convo-heading convo-reveal">
    The Intelligence Field manifesto<span class="convo-cursor"></span>
  </h2>

  <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
    <strong>Your conversations are brilliant. They just need memory.</strong> No more context switching across a pieced-together tool stack. No more rebuilding context every session. No more losing decisions to closed browser tabs.
  </p>

  <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
    Every AI conversation produces decisions, frameworks, and insights. We believe they should <strong>compound instead of disappearing</strong>.
  </p>

  <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
    Your agents need more than a folder. They need an office — with <em>memory, coordination, skills, and dispatch</em>.
  </p>

  <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
    We believe the future isn't about picking the right AI — it's about building the <strong>intelligence layer</strong> that makes every AI you use smarter. The vault remembers. The cards coordinate. The agents execute. And your field grows.
  </p>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- THE LAW OF RECURSION                        -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="convo-section convo-section--wide convo-reveal-group">
  <div class="convo-reveal">
    <div class="convo-speaker">
      <div class="convo-speaker__dot"></div>
      The cosmology
    </div>
    <div class="convo-divider"></div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="convo-heading convo-heading--large convo-reveal">
    The Law of Recursion<span class="convo-cursor"></span>
  </h2>

  <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
    Multiplist is built on a law older than software, older than cognition, older than story: <strong>the Law of Recursion</strong>. Recursion is how meaning forms itself. It is how intelligence deepens, how identity refines, how systems become coherent.
  </p>

  <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
    In human life, recursion appears as the ongoing conversation between two forces:
  </p>

  <div class="recursion-forces convo-reveal">
    <div class="recursion-force recursion-force--jupiter">
      <div class="recursion-force__symbol">♃</div>
      <h3 class="recursion-force__name">Jupiter — Expansion</h3>
      <p class="recursion-force__body">
        The part of you that dreams, imagines, questions, creates, intuits, and sees the world in patterns. We activate Jupiter through Fractal Twinning — surfacing your philosophy, your frameworks, your worldview, the signal beneath the noise.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="recursion-force recursion-force--saturn">
      <div class="recursion-force__symbol">♄</div>
      <h3 class="recursion-force__name">Saturn — Structure</h3>
      <p class="recursion-force__body">
        The part of you that builds, refines, systematizes, and turns ideas into form. We activate Saturn through the Multiplist platform — giving your intelligence architecture, modularity, and a foundation that scales.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="convo-body convo-reveal" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; font-style: italic; color: #a6a6a6;">
    Expansion → Structure → Expansion → Structure.<br>
    Each iteration increases coherence, precision, and expressive power.
  </p>

  <p class="convo-body convo-reveal" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 24px;">
    <strong style="color: #EAEAEA; font-size: 1.0625rem;">Multiplist is not software that assists human thinking.<br>It is the environment in which recursion becomes conscious.</strong>
  </p>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- ND-FIRST                                    -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="convo-platform convo-reveal-group">
  <div class="convo-platform__inner">
    <div class="convo-reveal">
      <div class="convo-speaker">
        <div class="convo-speaker__dot"></div>
        Our approach
      </div>
      <div class="convo-divider"></div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="convo-heading convo-reveal">
      ND-first by design<span class="convo-cursor"></span>
    </h2>

    <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
      Multiplist was built by a neurodivergent brain, for the way neurodivergent brains actually work. That means: async-first, visual-spatial, no unnecessary meetings, everything documented, and systems that catch things when your working memory doesn't.
    </p>

    <p class="convo-body convo-reveal">
      But here's the thing — <em>these principles make everything better for everyone</em>. Clear documentation, persistent context, structured knowledge, and systems that compound? That's not accommodation. That's just good architecture.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- FRACTAL TWINNING                            -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="convo-fractal convo-reveal-group">
